        "Answer": "As a common carrier, Jovencio is bound to observe **extraordinary diligence** in the vigilance over the safety of the passengers transported by them. Article 1755 of the Civil Code specifies that the common carrier should carry the passengers safely as far as human care and foresight can provide, using the **utmost diligence of very cautious persons**, with a due regard for all the circumstances."
