        "Question": "If a will is executed by a testator who was born a Filipino citizen but became naturalized Japanese citizen at the time of his death, what law will govern its testamentary provisions if the will is executed in China and the property being disposed is located in Indonesia? A) Chinese law B) Philippine law C) Indonesia law D) Japanese law.",
        "Answer": "D) Japanese law."
